                      ARAVT GLOBAL LLC
                    

•   NEW YORK, NY
                          • Investment Advisor
                          • Hedge Fund
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Aravt Global is based out of New York. Aravt Global is a hedge fund  with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $1,544,047,999 (Form ADV from 2017-03-31).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $1,367,904,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 93.85%. Aravt Global's largest holding is SPDR Gold Trust ETF with shares held of 3,000,000.   WhaleWisdom has at least 11 13F filings in our database for Aravt Global. 
                                           














